import React from 'react'
import { Container, Button } from '@material-ui/core'

export default function ReadingFooter() {
  <Container>
    <Link to="/spreads">
      <Button style={{ margin: 20 }} variant="contained" color="primary">
        Get another reading
        </Button>
    </Link>
    <Link to="/deck">
      <Button style={{ margin: 20 }} variant="contained" color="primary">
        See all the cards
        </Button>
    </Link>
  </Container>
}
